Package xxl.comparators

Provides some useful additional Comparators based on Comparator.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ComparableComparator The ComparableComparator uses the compareTo()-method of a given Comparable-Object to compare two elements.
EmbeddingComparator The EmbeddingComparator adds a bound to a given Comparator.
FeatureComparator The FeatureComparator compares the 'feature's of two given Objects.
InverseComparator The InverseComparator inverts the ordering of a given Comparator.
LexicographicalComparator The LexicographicalComparator creates a lexicographical ordering.
 

Package xxl.comparators Description

Provides some useful additional Comparators based on Comparator.
